rive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":72,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CJYCEM2rARgBIhMI5tGNxrfrkwMVslXyAB3PkydcSKLNs7qNv-3qEsoBBMoxucU=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa0FLdFVHck5zdWVnQWF4NWJMYWdUYVpKZ0NvQXxBQ3Jtc0tsWFRVcy1KLXZjbUExRlQxb1l4NjZKNndIY0o4RjBrQ2NYWDVqTjUybExkeWotdjlNT1NGR1prVTZwQlJMdnhlaWRocEhMTG9tQkxXc3FmdkJUMVB0cE5LMTlyQ1lBdDdmWUt2aGdYam8zZzlFVEg2Zw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=EtW1-NdM5qI","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa0FLdFVHck5zdWVnQWF4NWJMYWdUYVpKZ0NvQXxBQ3Jtc0tsWFRVcy1KLXZjbUExRlQxb1l4NjZKNndIY0o4RjBrQ2NYWDVqTjUybExkeWotdjlNT1NGR1prVTZwQlJMdnhlaWRocEhMTG9tQkxXc3FmdkJUMVB0cE5LMTlyQ1lBdDdmWUt2aGdYam8zZzlFVEg2Zw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=EtW1-NdM5qI","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":184,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CJYCEM2rARgBIhMI5tGNxrfrkwMVslXyAB3PkydcSKLNs7qNv-3qEsoBBMoxucU=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbVRwc3VUX1F3TDNGektVZE5jQlJVZ1pRMXdid3xBQ3Jtc0ttNVl3cWNZRzFBTVhjdVBIcm5heWF3WDVpRURzYk5McW40Zzl2emhVeTUtQXRmYWQwMHJQam5pZV9VMXZydVdBMzZTUXRSaXZLWDFvN05rcWdGeVNMN2IwWWF2Ul9ISzV2UmhxWl9jekFqTzBQdk1FZw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pay