: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":72,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBQQ040EGAYiEwjm0Y3Gt-uTAxWyVfIAHc-TJ1xIos2zuo2_7eoSygEEyjG5xQ==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa1cwMVJYYmhpZWtzZWNlNkpBeHZBZzRXMS04Z3xBQ3Jtc0tsNlI3aEVXRVN3UzRCb280bk5nU0RpY3NtV1B0TmRaVDZUZ0Q0YzVGaTZVQTRWYnpMc3RXUjNxbF9kaDZKY3hZNkltdWNFZjJ4SFhMNGJRV2RjdWdsRkExSndXLU9sN3RTTnZuZ01CM3RfUW00Zjl0UQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=EtW1-NdM5qI","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa1cwMVJYYmhpZWtzZWNlNkpBeHZBZzRXMS04Z3xBQ3Jtc0tsNlI3aEVXRVN3UzRCb280bk5nU0RpY3NtV1B0TmRaVDZUZ0Q0YzVGaTZVQTRWYnpMc3RXUjNxbF9kaDZKY3hZNkltdWNFZjJ4SFhMNGJRV2RjdWdsRkExSndXLU9sN3RTTnZuZ01CM3RfUW00Zjl0UQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=EtW1-NdM5qI","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":184,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBQQ040EGAYiEwjm0Y3Gt-uTAxWyVfIAHc-TJ1xIos2zuo2_7eoSygEEyjG5xQ==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa3ViaXVCbFpKUzU2c0UzcGNqNml0eUl2aDBkZ3xBQ3Jtc0ttTWUxekgtdElIZVF0U2FZRjlHamZiYlBYQWhWNTUySElhMVVxZ2R5WVl6OV8xbFBKUmYxZEtUNWltaUc4cWtJLVNRbVB0U0VRTUF6QnFkYTUzU01nZEFTYkk1UnhGRmcy